Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your usual? I forgot what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to remember, Robbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger, double cheese,\Nextra ketchup, thick-sliced tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Slip in pickles, and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That Chinese or Vietnamese dude,\Nhe's been nosing around about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes here a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He even asked me who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no Chinese or Vietnamese dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he's Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:01:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a neurosurgeon,\Nand a damn fine one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ex-fiancée was the daughter\Nof the director of your hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eva"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Ms. Heinemann" to you, pal!\NYou ain't engaged to her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only are you not a doctor\Nanymore but you're also a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to prison,\Nserve your time and start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a model inmate,\Nyou could even get out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Eva go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't holding her against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to parties every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't go trashing my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit hanging around here. Now get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a couple of days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should at least tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't beat him up, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're leaving.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done with today's party already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just for today. I'm done with parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How about having dinner with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you dropped her off\Nat some restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but you came here for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the food at those parties\Nand high-class restaurants,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the hamburgers here are way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure\Nif that's a compliment or an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get hurt again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to get--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You behind the counter, freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Move and I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a dangerous doctor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your boss is The Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But the man who ordered you to protect Eva
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is even higher up in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A man with glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he making Eva do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I told you,\Nhe's just having Eva go to parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She eats, drinks then leaves. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be doing\Nsomething special at those parties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come to think of it, today…\N-Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She pointed at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She pointed at someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She went like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and pointed at a young blonde man\Nwith a pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Eva now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's having dinner\Nwith that guy with glasses who hired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Tell me now! Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva's job is over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When this job is over,\NI'm sure I'll be murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent her to her hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No… I never carry a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, the party was just like\Nall the other ones we went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for that single moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva pointed at a certain young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the man with glasses showed up\Nwith another well-dressed young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the two young men shook hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:09:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice it at the time,\Nbut that was when Eva's job ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it would be you\Nwho would kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already gotten pretty drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no more regrets either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't shoot me at this hotel, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me how\Nwhen you shot your girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you found yourself\Nstanding in a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me outside when you shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't,\Nthey'll make you pay to clean the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still one thing that I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, I guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell did I do that today anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me, right? When I pointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet what I did today\Nwas pretty damn terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought together\Nsome horrible people with the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like bringing together Mephistopheles\Nand Faust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But who cares anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After what I did today,\NI won't be going to any more parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've still got all these invitations\Nto parties that are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm dead,\Nwhy don't you check up on what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,\Nyou may as well put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've got me all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away with you? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When did we get so close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't kill people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill people?\NBut could you kill a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That suit and necktie\Nthat I bought for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they're the same ones Kenzo wore long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?\NI dressed you up to look like Kenzo Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you kill me soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I could kill a devil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to sleep this off for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!\NYou'll die if you fall asleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Just leave me here a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure look gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I always look gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anyone come looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Japanese guy\Nleft this with me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hellblau Hotel Room 205."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to contact him there\Nif you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want your usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fill up on some disgusting hamburger,\NI'll lose the will to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crazy, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With just a single necktie,\Nthey'll let you in anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one of these…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that guy's a devil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He shook hands with so many people\Nthat his hand must be rubbed raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he left the party venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The sixth floor, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But which room is he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to meet him too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for him too.\NHe'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk a little until he arrives.\NLet's see, what should we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The young punk happily blabbered on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked like a child\Nspeaking to his parents
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,about the fun he had at school that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He just kept talking to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"The end of the world," my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The crazy young punk's talk\Nwas a bunch of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?\NPretty interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy it, Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an idea. Let's talk about you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working for The Baby\Nfor three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been looking into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, you were in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those must have been a hard eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a model inmate though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You got out pretty quickly\Nfor having been a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy living with your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the girlfriend you shot\Nand killed. Her name was Edda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got pretty poor taste, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a total drug addict, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You did everything you could\Nto get her off drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you did it out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She got back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd make you dinner\Nand wait for you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You started living a happy life together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to punch your lights out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But one night, when you got home,\Nyou saw something that blew your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ex-boyfriend was at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd done drugs again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and while in a daze,\Nshe said to you over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry…"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But you shot and killed\Nboth her and the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that's how it came out in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She killed herself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she had gunshot residue on her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,your lawyer figured\Nshe had killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However,\Nyou insisted that you had shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked you to kill her, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullseye! I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.\NIt wasn't you who shot her, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet this is what she said, "Shoot me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me! Please kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it! She shot herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It wasn't me! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?\NAmazing! I got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave her what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're wrong.\N-Then what about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother froze to death\Nwhen you were ten years old, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserted your mother too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right about that too! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.\NI can really see these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, you carried your\Nalcoholic mother back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?\NYour mother would always tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Leave me here."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you carried her home every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But one night…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't sleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?\NYou left your mother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, you were notified\Nthat your mother froze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is what you thought then,\N"It wasn't my fault."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"I only did that\Nbecause she asked me to leave her there."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly right.\NIt wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Both your mother and\Nyour drug-addict girlfriend wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These people wanted to die,\Nso you simply let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything wrong.\NWhat you did was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You released them from the misery of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva too. She wants to die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, the devil came.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't look at the devil\Nas we passed by one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated that\Nto myself like a child would.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by: Brian Athey
